__________
using WHEN
__________
What when Actually Does
It tells Ansible:
“Run this task ONLY IF this condition is true.”


---
- name: Install nginx on Ubuntu
  apt:
    name: nginx
    state: present
  when: ansible_facts['os_family'] == "Debian"

- name: Install nginx on RedHat
  yum:
    name: nginx
    state: present
  when: ansible_facts['os_family'] == "RedHat"


(OR)

advanced way

---
- name: Install nginx
  package:
    name: nginx
    state: present


















